    "## Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "✅ **What you learned:**\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **PINN Architecture**: Simple MLP with Tanh activations\n",
    "2. **Physics Loss**: Mean squared ODE residual using autograd\n",
    "3. **Initial Loss**: Enforce initial condition at t=0\n",
    "4. **Training Loop**: Standard PyTorch optimization\n",
    "5. **Evaluation**: L2 error, residual analysis\n",
